parameters:
Innkeeper: "I got my hands on some top-notch
liquor recently~ How about you join me for a drink
sometime, Eva-san~"
SV_PLAY_VOICE エヴァ_宿屋まわり/エヴァ_宿屋まわり-01 90 100 0 2

Eva: "Um, well... I'm not very good with
alcohol..."
SV_PLAY_VOICE ティア_宿屋まわり/ティア_宿屋まわり-01 90 100 0 2

Innkeeper's Daughter: "Hey, Dad! You're making
Eva-san uncomfortable, aren't you!?"
SV_PLAY_VOICE ティア_宿屋まわり/ティア_宿屋まわり-02 90 100 0 2
SV_PLAY_VOICE リィナ_宿屋まわり/リィナ_宿屋まわり-01 90 100 0 2

Riina: "It's going to be a problem if Mom gets
drunk"
SV_PLAY_VOICE ティア_宿屋まわり/ティア_宿屋まわり-03 90 100 0 2
Innkeeper: "Ah, Tia is so naggy, it's troublesome"
SV_PLAY_VOICE エヴァ_宿屋まわり/エヴァ_宿屋まわり-02 90 100 0 2

Eva: "Hehehe... Tia-chan is so responsible, she's
such a good girl, isn't she?"
SV_PLAY_VOICE エヴァ_宿屋まわり/エヴァ_宿屋まわり-03 90 100 0 2
Eva: "I wish my Riina would be more like Tia-chan"
SV_PLAY_VOICE リィナ_宿屋まわり/リィナ_宿屋まわり-02 90 100 0 2
SV_PLAY_VOICE ティア_宿屋まわり/ティア_宿屋まわり-04 90 100 0 2
SV_PLAY_VOICE リーザ_宿屋まわり/リーザ_宿屋まわり-01 90 100 0 2
SV_PLAY_VOICE ティア_宿屋まわり/ティア_宿屋まわり-05 90 100 0 2
SV_PLAY_VOICE リーザ_宿屋まわり/リーザ_宿屋まわり-02 90 100 0 2

Reeza: "Well then, I'm off to patrol the village
today! When I get back, I'm counting on a
delicious meal, Tia-chan♪"
SV_PLAY_VOICE ティア_宿屋まわり/ティア_宿屋まわり-06 90 100 0 2

Tia: "Yes, leave it to me! Good luck out there,
Reeza-san♪"
SV_PLAY_VOICE リーザ_宿屋まわり/リーザ_宿屋まわり-03 90 100 0 2
SV_PLAY_VOICE エヴァ_宿屋まわり/エヴァ_宿屋まわり-04 90 100 0 2
Eva: "Riina, let's go with Reeza-san too"
SV_PLAY_VOICE リィナ_宿屋まわり/リィナ_宿屋まわり-03 90 100 0 2
Riina: "Ehh~ I still want to play with Tia-chan~"
SV_PLAY_VOICE エヴァ_宿屋まわり/エヴァ_宿屋まわり-05 90 100 0 2

Eva: "Now, now, that's enough. We'll come again
when we have time, okay?"
SV_PLAY_VOICE リィナ_宿屋まわり/リィナ_宿屋まわり-04 90 100 0 2
SV_PLAY_VOICE リィナ_宿屋まわり/リィナ_宿屋まわり-05 90 100 0 2
SV_PLAY_VOICE ティア_宿屋まわり/ティア_宿屋まわり-07 90 100 0 2
SV_PLAY_VOICE エヴァ_宿屋まわり/エヴァ_宿屋まわり-06 90 100 0 2
SV_PLAY_VOICE リーザ_宿屋まわり/リーザ_宿屋まわり-04 90 100 0 2
Reeza: "Of course! I'll escort you home!"
SV_PLAY_VOICE リィナ_宿屋まわり/リィナ_宿屋まわり-06 90 100 0 2
SV_PLAY_VOICE エヴァ_宿屋まわり/エヴァ_宿屋まわり-07 90 100 0 2
Eva: "Then we'll be on our way now"

Innkeeper: "Eva-san is truly wonderful, isn't
she~"

Tia: "Like Eva-san would ever bother with someone
like Dad..."
Innkeeper: "No, no, that's not true at all"

Innkeeper: "I think Eva-san must be lonely too,
after losing her husband"

Innkeeper: "You'd be happy if Riina-chan was your
sister, right?"

Tia: "Well, yes, but... Dad with Eva-san is just
impossible"

Innkeeper: "No, if there's even a slight
chance..."
Tia: "Ah~, yes yes, I got it, I got it"

Tia: "Come on, if Eva-san comes by, work's not
getting done anyway, so at least work properly
now, okay?"
Ruth: "(Is this Eva someone who's a female elf?)"

Ruth: "(If that's the case, that old man is quite
out of his league)"
Tia: "...The monsters won't come again, right?"
Innkeeper: "Reeza-san will take care of it."
Innkeeper: "Yeah, so let's carry on as usual."
Tia: "By the way, Dad looked kinda cool earlier."

Innkeeper: "If anything happens to Tia, Dad will
protect you properly!"

Ruth: "(For now, it seems calm inside... Let's try
to avoid doing anything reckless...)"

Ruth: "(Well, even though I say that, there might
be times when I have to do something reckless...)"

Tia: "I wish someone would just get rid of them
quickly!"

Innkeeper: "Ah, we need Reeza-san to work hard on
this!"

Ruth: "(It seems things have calmed down inside
for now...)"

Ruth: "Eva's doing a good job of distracting the
old man."

Ruth: "Now I just need to sneak in through the
back door..."

Ruth: "With this, I can safely use the back
entrance."
Ruth: "All that's left is to break in..."
